videos.description: Facundo Campazzo runs the fast break and throws a sweet underhanded pass through traffic to Vlatko Cancar for the easy finish at the rim.

videos.description: Nikola Jokic puts up 28 points, 19 rebounds and 9 assists, but ends up being ejected from the game after a heated exchange with the referees in the Nuggets' 113-107 win over thee Wizards.
